Call of Duty Modern Warfare - Gunfire Mode Weapons


Gunfire Mode features two teams of two players
facing off in multiple rounds — the first to six wins the game.

Every two rounds a new set of random guns and equipment
is chosen and all four players must use those weapons.


The diagram simulates the random selection of weapons
throughout 11 rounds (the maximum possible).

Before each set of 2 rounds, 2 random weapons are selected.

Once the weapons are established, the rounds are "played"
and after every 2nd round of each set,
the set rounds counter returns to 0
and the process begins again.
